//[Reference] 'So I was thinking about how we could improve the local farmlands.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10000100=我之前一直在思考，我們應該如何去改善當地的農田。
//[Reference] 'Our first step should be to improve crop yield.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10000200=第一步，我們應該提升作物產量。
//[Reference] 'After that we'll try out this new formula I invented...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10000300=在那之後，我們可以試試這個我發明的新配方……
//[Reference] 'Are you even listening?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10000400=你有在聽我說嗎？
//[Reference] 'Just the other day I rolled out a new cultivator.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10000500=就在前幾天，我剛弄了一台新的耕田機。
//[Reference] 'I was going to show you but the mayor confiscated it...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10000600=我本來打算給你瞧瞧，可是鎮長把它沒收了……
//[Reference] 'And here it would have made your work so much easier too...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10000700=本來它會讓你的工作變得更輕鬆……
//[Reference] 'Don't go drinking bottles you find lying around...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10000800=別喝你在地上撿到的瓶子裡的東西……
//[Reference] 'Some of those chemicals do nasty things to a person.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10000900=有些化學物質對人體不太好。
//[Reference] 'Not that I'm speaking from experience of course...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10001000=當然，這並不是我的經驗之談……
//[Reference] '^c:d03e37;Seedmakers^c:pop; are fantastic aren't they?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10001100=^c:d03e37;種子製造機^c:pop;非常棒，對吧？
//[Reference] 'Sometimes you can end up with rare variants!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10001200=有時候你還能獲得一些稀有的變異種子！
//[Reference] 'I wonder if I can rig one to produce them more often...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10001300=不知道我能不能搞一台，多弄點變異種子……
//[Reference] 'Just to be clear...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10001400=我要說明一點……
//[Reference] 'It's professor, not doctor.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10001500=我是教授，可不是博士。
//[Reference] 'Professor ^c:1486b0;{0-name}^c:pop;.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10001600=^c:1486b0;{0-name}^c:pop;教授。
//[Reference] 'Don't mix them up.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10001700=可別弄混了。
//[Reference] '^c:1486b0;{0-shopkeep}^c:pop; has been giving me strange looks recently...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10001800=^c:1486b0;{0-shopkeep}^c:pop;最近總用奇怪的眼光來看我……
//[Reference] 'Did I do something to cause offence?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10001900=我做了什麼冒犯之事嗎？
//[Reference] 'I'm a bit sceptical about that magic water...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10002000=我有一點懷疑那個魔法之水……
//[Reference] 'I don't know where it came from or how it works...'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10002100=我不知道它是從哪兒來的，也不知道它的原理是什麼……
//[Reference] 'But, there's no way magic is a real thing.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10002200=可是，魔法什麼的，是不存在的。
//[Reference] 'How do airships work, you ask?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10002300=你是問，飛船是怎麼運作的嗎？
//[Reference] 'Well then! That's a fascinating topic.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10002400=那好吧！這是個讓人著迷的話題啊。
//[Reference] 'You see, we build the hull from an ultralight super-material.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10002500=你瞧，我們用超輕型材料來製造船體。
//[Reference] 'The rotors-'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10002600=而回轉軸——
//[Reference] 'Wood? What? Where did you hear that?'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10002700=是木頭的？什麼？你從哪兒聽來這個的？
//[Reference] 'It just looks like wood! It's not really wood!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10002800=它只是看起來像木頭！這可不是真的木頭！
//[Reference] 'There's no such thing as magic!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10002900=世界上根本沒有魔法！
//[Reference] 'Rainy days are such a great energy saver!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10003000=雨天會非常的節能！
//[Validate] Delete this comment if or when the translation is accurate.
//[Reference] 'I can turn off all my sprinkler systems.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10003100=我可以關閉所有的噴水系統。
//[Reference] 'The rain does all the watering for me!'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10003200=完全可以僅靠雨水幫我澆灌！
//[Reference] 'If you want to know how the lights work, I can't help you.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10003300=如果你想知道光是怎麼工作的，那我就幫不了你了。
//[Reference] 'Countless research projects have proven fruitless.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10003400=無數的研究項目最終都毫無結果。
//[Reference] 'We disproved the existence of the luminiferous aether.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10003500=而我們證明了以太是不存在的。
//[Reference] 'There is no light emitting photon energy source.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10003600=沒有光會發射光子能量源。
//[Reference] 'And it is definitely. Not. Magic.'
staxel.village.dialogue.Scientist.line:10003700=而且這絕、對、不、是、魔、法！
